1. *Pijana* sam sinoć popila previše. (I drank too much last night.)
2. Ona je bila *pijana* kada je došla kući. (She was drunk when she came home.)
3. *Pijani* vozač je izazvao saobraćajnu nesreću. (The drunk driver caused a car accident.)
4. Muškarac je *pijan* pao na ulici. (The man fell down on the street drunk.)
5. Njena prijateljica se *opijala* čitave noći. (Her friend was getting drunk all night long.)
6. Nikad ne vozite *pod uticajem alkohola*. (Never drive under the influence of alcohol.)
7. Oni su *opijeni* mirisom mora. (They are intoxicated by the smell of the sea.)
8. Kada je vidio koliko je popio, shvatio je da je već *pijan*. (When he saw how much he had drunk, he realized he was already drunk.)
9. Grupa mladića je bila *pijana* i glasna na ulici. (A group of young men were drunk and loud on the street.)
10. Baka je bila *pripita* nakon čaše vina za ručak. (Grandma was tipsy after a glass of wine with lunch.)